# Input

```scss
@at-root(without:media   supports){
.root-only{
color:red;
}
}

@at-root
.root-only,
.another-root
{
color:blue;
}

@mixin card{
@at-root(with:rule){
.card{
display:block;
}
}
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@at-root (without: media supports) {
	.root-only {
		color: red;
	}
}

@at-root .root-only, .another-root {
	color: blue;
}

@mixin card {
	@at-root (with: rule) {
		.card {
			display: block;
		}
	}
}

```
